Parameters.name: Dry
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the volume of the unaffected sound.

FX.name: Ba PDLPit
FX.description: Use an expression pedal to change the pitch in real time with this effect.

Parameters.name: Bend
Parameters.explanation: Sets the amount of pitch shift.

Parameters.name: Color
Parameters.explanation: Sets the type of pitch change control with the expression pedal.

FX.name: Ba PDLMnP
FX.description: This is a pitch shifter specially for monophonic sound (single-note playing), which allows the pitch to be shifted in real time with the expression pedal.

Parameters.name: Bend
Parameters.explanation: Sets the amount of pitch shift.

Parameters.name: Color
Parameters.explanation: Sets the type of pitch change control with the expression pedal.

FX.name: Output VP
FX.description: This controls the product output level. This volume will be kept even when the patch is changed.
